# Customer Churn Prediction – ML Engineering Project

## Problem
Predict whether a customer will churn based on historical usage and contract data.

## Objective
Build a reproducible ML pipeline and deploy a trained model as a REST API.

## Tech Stack
- Python
- pandas, scikit-learn, XGBoost
- Docker
- AWS EC2 + S3
- FastAPI

## Project Status
Phase 0 – Project setup
